{
  "text": "Ultrasound-guided percutaneous tracheostomy (US-PCT) is a safe, easy, and fast method in several populations, including obese patients [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . However, to our knowledge, there are no published data on US-PCT in patients with tetanus. We have just performed the first US-PCT on a patient with tetanus.",
  "citation_candidates": [
